When exporting issues via JSON exporter, we will get user details at the end of the JSON data. The data should look something like below:
{noformat}
"users" : [ {
    "name" : "support",
    "fullname" : "support",
    "email" : "support@mail.com",
    "groups" : [ "jira-users", "jira-developers" ],
    "active" : true
  }, {
    "name" : "user",
    "fullname" : "user",
    "email" : "user@mail.com",
    "groups" : [ "jira-users" ],
    "active" : true
  }, {
    "name" : "admin",
